OL,3,CPolice discover #2m worth of cannabis
OL,4,Cplants in old school building
OL,6,FTwo men have admitted to drug charges
OL,7,Fafter around 1,500 cannabis plants,
OL,8,Fworth nearly #2 million, were
OL,9,Fdiscovered at a former school in
OL,10,FLlandysul, Ceredigion.
OL,12,FDyfed-Powys Police were alerted to the
OL,13,Fhaul after carrying out a stop check
OL,14,Fon a car travelling through
OL,15,FCarmarthenshire on July 4. Inside the
OL,16,Fcar, officers found five suitcases
OL,17,Ffilled with cannabis.
OL,19,FTwo men, who had travelled from London
OL,20,Fto Ceredigion, were then arrested.
