OL,6,FThe force's investigation led to the
OL,7,Fformer school building on Marble
OL,8,FTerrace in Llandysul, where the large
OL,9,Fsupply of cannabis plants were
OL,10,Fdiscovered across two floors.
OL,12,FThe total street value of the cannabis
OL,13,Fbud and plants seized would have been
OL,14,Fup to #1,960,000.
OL,16,FAlfred Perkola, 43, from Ealing,
OL,17,FLondon, and Adli Gjegjaj, 25 of
OL,18,FSalford, were charged with being
OL,19,Fconcerned in the production of
OL,20,Fcannabis, with Perkola also charged
OL,21,Fwith possession with intent to supply.
