OL,6,FBoth men admitted the offences when
OL,7,Fthey appeared at court on Saturday (6
OL,8,FJuly).
OL,10,FDetective Chief Inspector Rich Lewis
OL,11,Fsaid: "This was a very successful
OL,12,Foperation, which saw excellent joint
OL,13,Fworking not only between a number of
OL,14,Fdepartments within Dyfed-Powys Police,
OL,15,Fbut also with other forces.
OL,17,F"We are committed to making our force
OL,18,Farea hostile to those who deal illegal
OL,19,Fdrugs, and our work over the weekend
OL,20,Fhas seen a significant amount of
OL,21,Fcannabis taken out of the supply chain.
